content: It seems to be a good trip if you go with children.
There are many Korean handicrafts here. I personally like handicrafts since I was a child. So let's see, but the price is not cheap, so I didn't buy many kinds of handicrafts.
There are many Korean folk arts and crafts exhibitions, many wooden things, as well as wood carvings.
Special museum, very comfortable place, like the atmosphere here, very comfortable.

The Art Museum is a traditional exhibition area of Korean crafts. There are many places specially responsible for selling some Korean specialty cuisine. Korean clothing is also exquisite. It feels very troublesome to wear.
Maybe it has lost a lot of children's fun. The children like me very much, but they can't feel it.
Very distinctive place, which incorporates Korean traditional elements, good
This craft venue is all handcrafted Korean crafts. It sells at a high price. Some people buy it, but it's not very cost-effective. Many things are rough.

At the automatic ticket collection office, there is always a large group of people busy collecting tickets. They take all the tickets at once. There are many kinds of exhibitions here, which are very good.
It's worth visiting, enjoying its fun, sculpture, puppet, eye-opening and knowledge at the same time. The environment is good and the facilities are good.
Museum is very large, the environment is very good, showing many modern arts and crafts, often have performances.
Some arts and crafts can be purchased. The price is too expensive. Just have a look.
